The postmaster has received a commission from Midgaard's registry office for a complete cartographic survey of Kowloon. The registry's documentation on the delta city is overdue for an update, and the current records fail to reflect recent changes to the city's district layout and harbor approaches. Walk every accessible section of Kowloon and return when your survey is complete.
Your cartographic survey of Kowloon has been filed with Midgaard's registry office. The updated city record has been accepted into the civic reference archive, and the postmaster has noted that this is the most complete documentation of Kowloon's layout that the registry has received in some time.

